    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250260/extras/c73d9cd451ec5b26bca2b10a0e5a450b.avif?t=1771150711\" width=1560 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Super Mario 64 meets Fall Guys.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself and your opponents in this rage platformer with a unique and wide variety of movement options.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you enjoy the game in multiplayer, where your friends become your greatest foes, or in solo-mode, where your only opponents are gravity and your own temper - once you enter the Planes only skill and patience will get you to the top.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250260/extras/a239382ac6fd6ca01ca66e96d0e18a7a.avif?t=1771150711\" width=1560 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>An unexpected journey lies ahead.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A specific focus on difficult and complex movement as well as carefully designed obstacles meant to synergize with the unique movement provides a party gaming experience not found in any other multiplayer platformers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250260/extras/7a0fab0e74d1cdae45911747c16c0f49.avif?t=1771150711\" width=1560 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Invite your friends to a challenge to see who will master traversing the planes and who will be left behind.</strong> <br><br>A variety of game modes, from elimination and race based maps to point based games awaits you to rank against your opponents and emerge as victor. Pick or vote for a map each round that suits your skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250260/extras/b0438ea4a96351d50b8338db7767f5e9.avif?t=1771150711\" width=1560 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In Singleplayer the only enemy you will face is yourself.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Without skill and patience you won't be able to reach the top in these large and vertical beasts of a map, where a single misstep can send you all the way to the bottom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250260/extras/803986758b742d243de8087ee0ba057a.avif?t=1771150711\" width=1560 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick from an ever expanding pool of clothes and cosmetics to face the challenges ahead of you with style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Download now and join the fray.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>P.S.:</strong> This will always be a handcrafted game without AI slop and without microtransactions or other questionable monetization methods.</p>",
